  <brief_title>Treatment of Granuloma Umbilical in Newborn Babies</brief_title>
  <official_title>Treatment of Granuloma Umbilical in Newborn Babies - Comparison of Treatment With Silver Nitrate Versus Alcohol Swaps Versus Steroid Creme Group IV</official_title>
