  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to show that steroid creme and even better alcohol swaps are just as
      effective or equal to the current treatment with silver nitrate of granuloma umbilical in
      newborns.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The change of treatment will make it possible for parents to treat the children themselves at
      home, whereas treatment with silver nitrate only is an in hospital regimen.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
